description.narrative: During 2019, UNICEF worked with partners and communities to guarantee safe water and sanitation for children and their families in North-East Syria. 59,360 people benefited from provision of water through establishing surface water system and 86,131 people including women and children, received WASH Non-Food Items (NFIs), including Family Hygiene Kits and water storage solution. | Status:Constrained | As-of Date:09/04/2020
